Emil - Tavern Brawl and Brand New Heroes – Now Available for Hearthstone

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*****************************************************************************

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Greetings Emil,

Trouble is brewing in the tavern. Patch 2.7 has arrived to Hearthstone™ bringing with it three new heroes to collect and the appearance of the elusive fourth button. Tavern Brawl flips the table on your typical Hearthstone game, putting an exciting and unexpected new spin on the rules every week! There’s no telling what will change, so be sure to visit each Wednesday to see what new challenge waits.  
