NEW HEROES

Is Garrosh too hot-tempered, or Jaina a little too chilly for you? Fear not, 3 new heroes are coming to Hearthstone with new portraits, animations, and emotes: Magni Bronzebeard (Warrior), Medivh (Mage), and Alleria Windrunner (Hunter).

Find out more  
